Volume Flow on Sonosite Edge II 

1. Obtain view of artery / fistula.
2. COLOR (C) mode. Adjust color box, make sure to insonate entire vessel.  
3. Press DOPPLER button, then FREEZE waveform.  
4. Press CALC.  
5. Select TAP. Vertical lines/calipers will appear. 
6. Position first line at beginning of waveform and click SELECT.  
7. Position second  line at end of waveform and click SELECT.  
8. Then select SET.  

==> Volume flow calculation will appear.  

